DTSTAMP:20260311T143800Z
DTSTART:20260317T103000
DTEND:20260317T123000
SUMMARY:Morning Figure Drawing at Artspace
LOCATION:Artspace\, 2833-A Hathaway Rd\, Richmond\, VA 23225
DESCRIPTION:Figure Drawing sessions every third Tuesday of the month. Draw a live model for 2 hours. Open session\, all skill levels welcome. Must be over 18. Bring your own drawing materials/board/easel.\\n\\nCost: $10 donation\\n\\nRegister: https://www.artspacegallery.org/upcoming-events/morning-figure-drawing-at-artspace-march-5xs8d-bwatp-nlkap-6jlcf-fsxet-63hw3-sz6kp-mybdb
