BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:2026-03-17-1800-studiotwothree@rvafiguredrawing
DTSTAMP:20260311T143800Z
DTSTART:20260317T180000
DTEND:20260317T210000
SUMMARY:Figure Drawing Night
LOCATION:Studio Two Three\, 109 W 15th St Richmond\, VA 23224
DESCRIPTION:3-hour figure drawing workshop with a professional nude model. Instructor Carter Helmandollar calls poses starting with short gestural poses and concluding with longer poses. Bring your own drawing/painting/sculpting materials.\\n\\nCost: $20\\n\\nRegister: https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-night
URL:https://www.studiotwothree.org/classes/p/figure-drawing-night
END:VEVENT
